sentences: Marina Kuroki (黒木 マリナ, Kuroki Marina, born 26 September 1988) is a Japanese actress, singer and model best known for her appearances in the Sailor Moon musicals series.
She starred in the Sailor Moon musicals as the lead role of Usagi Tsukino at the age of 12 and finished her Sailor Moon career at 16 in 2005.
She recently moved to J-Pop and sang songs used in various anime Series.
